| 2026-05-21 | F-172 | **Session 45 — M1 pipeline page responsiveness v2 (funnel overflow, sticky sidebar, collapsed footer).** Four UI issues on `/admin/m1/pipeline`: (1) funnel chart bars overflowed card by 100× — `widthPct = (value / counts[TIERS[0].key]) * 100` divides by *ingested*; once rows drained downstream (`ingested=1, extracted=101, preprocessed=102`) math produced 10,100% widths; (2) chunky native scrollbar visible in sidebar — earlier fix scoped `* {scrollbar:none}` to `html,body` only, exposing sidebar's `overflow-y-auto`; (3) sidebar scrolled with page instead of pinning — previous fix used `overflow-x-hidden` on admin layout flex containers; `overflow:hidden` on any axis establishes a containing block that disables `position:sticky` on descendants; (4) collapsed sidebar's user/locale footer cramped. Fixes: funnel uses `maxAcrossTiers = Math.max(1, ...TIERS.map(t => counts[t.key] ?? 0))` denominator + clamps `widthPct` to `[0,100]` + adds `overflow-hidden` + `bg-muted/30` on track parent; sidebar gets `scrollbar-hide` class on inner `<nav>` + tighter `mx-1.5` collapsed card margin + `p-1.5` collapsed bottom-section padding; `UserRow` rewritten to branch on `collapsed` — stack avatar above logout pill with `<Tooltip>`-wrapped triggers when collapsed, horizontal row with hover bg when expanded, avatar gets `ring-1 ring-border/60`; admin layout switches `overflow-x-hidden` → `overflow-x-clip` on both flex container + main column. | `enigmatrix-frontend/components/m1-pipeline/funnel-chart.tsx` · `enigmatrix-frontend/components/layout/sidebar.tsx` · `enigmatrix-frontend/app/(admin)/layout.tsx` |
| 2026-05-21 | F-171 | **Session 44 — Theme polish (view-transition animation smoothness + disable system tracking).** Two unrelated theme issues. (1) View-transition reveal felt twitchy — `startViewTransition` clip-path animation used `ease-in-out` over 420 ms, and the universal `* { transition: ... }` rule in `globals.css` was running underneath the view-transition snapshot producing two parallel animations. (2) App auto-changed theme when OS flipped colour scheme. Fixes: `theme-toggle.tsx` easing → `cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1)` (easeOutQuint), duration 420 ms → 600 ms, subtle scale (1.015→1) + opacity (0.92→1) on new layer, scale (1→0.985) + opacity (1→0.6) on old layer; flip `theme-transitioning` class on `<html>` for transition's lifetime; sync Sun/Moon icon transitions to 500 ms with same bezier. `globals.css` adds GPU promotion (`will-change: clip-path, transform, opacity`, `backface-visibility: hidden`, `transform-origin: center center`) on `::view-transition-old/new(root)` + `html.theme-transitioning *` rule suppressing universal colour transitions during the view-transition window. `providers.tsx` `ThemeProvider` props: `defaultTheme="system"` → `defaultTheme="light"`, added `enableSystem={false}`, added `storageKey="enigmatrix-theme"`. Confirmed via grep that `setTheme` is only invoked from `theme-toggle.tsx`. | `enigmatrix-frontend/components/layout/theme-toggle.tsx` · `enigmatrix-frontend/app/globals.css` · `enigmatrix-frontend/components/providers.tsx` |
